OL,3,CBritish Airways flight attendant found
OL,4,C'naked and high on drugs' in plane
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FA British Airways flight attendant was
OL,8,Ffound "high on drugs and completely
OL,9,Fnaked" in an onboard toilet during a
OL,10,Fflight from California to London, a
OL,11,Fcourt has heard.
OL,13,FHaden Pentecost, 41, was described as
OL,14,Fagitated, sweating and babbling when
OL,15,Fhe was found by a colleague.
OL,17,FHe had to be stood down by the
OL,18,Fflight's manager when he failed to
OL,19,Fhelp with any pre-flight safety checks.
