OL,3,CBritish Airways flight attendant found
OL,4,C'naked and high on drugs' in plane
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FAfter complaining of stomach cramps
OL,8,Fand saying he needed to change his
OL,9,Fclothes, the air steward locked
OL,10,Fhimself in one of the plane's
OL,11,Fbathrooms.
OL,13,FWhen he opened the door, his colleague
OL,14,Fsaid he was oblivious to the fact that
OL,15,Fhe had no clothes on. She had to dress
OL,16,Fhim before moving him into a free
OL,17,Fseat, the court was told.
