OL,3,CBritish Airways flight attendant found
OL,4,C'naked and high on drugs' in plane
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FThe flight attendant was spoken to by
OL,8,Fthe captain before a health
OL,9,Fprofessional was called for,
OL,10,Fmagistrates were told.
OL,12,FHe had dilated pupils, a high heart
OL,13,Frate, and had to be checked every 20
OL,14,Fminutes until the plane arrived at
OL,15,FHeathrow ` where paramedics took him
OL,16,Fto hospital.
OL,18,FA blood test revealed Pentecost had
OL,19,Fmethamphetamine and amphetamine in his
OL,20,Fsystem, the court heard.
