OL,12,FPentecost appeared at Uxbridge
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Friday, where he
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to performing an
OL,15,Faviation function while impaired by
OL,16,Fdrugs.
OL,18,FHe has since been sacked by British
OL,19,FAirways, the court was told.
